description:
It's "Super Pi Day." OR IS IT?

Last Year's anti-pi rant: https://youtu.be/5iUh_CSjaSw?list=PL5F03A9D6D278C5D9
Original "Pi is (still) Wrong" video: https://youtu.be/jG7vhMMXagQ?list=PL5F03A9D6D278C5D9
This year's Pi Day Anthem: https://youtu.be/NsKH5h7j2_o?list=PL5F03A9D6D278C5D9

Next year is Engineer's Pi Day, so called because we properly round the digits instead of truncating them. The name was coined by Artery Lines on facebook! https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=867123683333759&id=154711904574944&comment_id=867310949981699&offset=0&total_comments=17
